LifeKnot is a social networking website with a focus on shared interests and hobbies. It was founded in November 2003 by Matt Muro, is based in Cambridge, MA and is privately owned.
The site has been noted twice in The Sunday Times, Get clicking with a like-minded stranger, Social whirl online; the Gothamist, LifeKnot: The New Online Meeting Place; the Denver Post, Internet hookups lead to recreation - and romance; and the Boston Herald.
